Requirements
------------

Flask
PyMongo


Installation
-----------

Update <YOUR SITE URL> in hooks/post-commit
Update <YOUR SITE URL> in server/app.py
Update pymongo db credentials in server/app.py
Copy hooks/post-commit into <git repo>/.git/hooks/

Running on Apache
-----------------

Update <PATH TO SERVER DIRECTORY> in server/wsgiapp.wsgi
Have apache look at server/wsgiapp.wsgi
